room_title: Escape room "Apartment 13" by Curiosity Escape Rooms in Hattiesburg
room_description: The year is 1973. You work as an investigative journalist for The Daily Post in Milwaukee, Wisconsin. You have been assigned the task of looking into the murder cases of three victims that were never solved. Several leads guide you to the Rindstone Apartments in downtown, specifically Apartment 13. After casing the joint, you find that the resident of the apartment is always gone from 3pm-4pm. Can you find evidence leading to the murder victims before the apartmentâ€™s resident returns and adds you to his list?
